title: Bold Playoff Predictions, Revisiting Preseason Predictions (Football 1/2)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough for a predictions episode. First, the guys make bold playoff predictions for the upcoming playoffs (4:15). Then, the Pick Six Superfriends revisit their preseason predictions for the 2019 NFL season (13:45), assessing what went right (but mostly wrong) with their September assessments.
